Usage : listdir string directoryName

After run this code , created  2 new file that are called as "total.txt" and "log.log".
The "log.log" txt is result file.
The "total.txt" i s helper file not important after running.

when you run this code "make clean". This "total.txt" file listdir and .o file is cleaned.

***                                 ***                                             ***
***                                 ***                                             ***
	The file that is called "log.log" is created as append mode in the code. Because of that the file must be deleted before scond running.
